flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B[Choose input type: URL, Text, or Headline]
    B --> C[Validate input]
    C -->|Invalid| D[Show validation error]
    D --> B
    C -->|Valid| E[POST /api/analyze]
    E --> F{Input type URL?}
    F -->|Yes| G[Fetch article content]
    F -->|No| H[Use provided text/headline]
    G --> I[Normalize analysis text]
    H --> I
    I --> J[Run NLP classifier]
    J --> K[Extract signal phrases]
    K --> L[Run fact-check claims search]
    L --> M[Score source credibility]
    M --> N[Aggregate verdict and credibility score]
    N --> O[Store analysis record in DB]
    O --> P[Cache response]
    P --> Q[Return AnalyzeResponse JSON]
    Q --> R[Render verdict cards and history item]
    R --> S([End])
    
